LA ROCHE-POSAY IN THE NEWS
From Award Winners for "Best In Beauty" to everyday skincare tips, La Roche-Posay is an editor favorite!







Offers






















Toleriane
Daily Cleansers & Moisturizers
Daily cleansers and moisturizers replenish essential moisture for hydrated, healthy looking skin. Developed under a strict formulation charter with carefully-selected ingredients, the Toleriane range of products are allergy tested, fragrance free, and paraben free.Discover our NEW Toleriane products below. 










Home








Skin Care







Product Lines






Toleriane



















What is the Skin Barrier?
Skin has a barrier which acts as the body’s first line of defense against external aggressors. It also helps retain essential moisture. Constant exposure to elements such as UV rays, pollution & stress can weaken the skin barrier.











Replenish Moisture
Keeping skin hydrated is key for healthy looking skin. Ingredients such as Glycerin and water can replenish moisture. La Roche-Posay Prebiotic Thermal Water has a unique combination of minerals & trace elements to soothe & hydrate skin.











Help Restore the Skin Barrier
Ceramides are a key component of skin. They help to make up the skin barrier and lock in moisture. Ceramides are naturally lost, which can contribute to dry skin. Replenishing these essential lipids is important for maintaining a strong skin barrier.




















NEW Toleriane Daily Moisturizers and Cleansers!

Introducing a new generation of cleansers and moisturizers that work together to help restore healthy looking skin. These gentle formulas replenish moisture and help restore skin’s natural protective barrier.
The new Toleriane products are formulated with La Roche-Posay Prebiotic Thermal Water, lipid-replenishing Ceramide-3, soothing Niacinamide, and moisturizing Glycerin.
Developed under a stringent formulation charter: oil free, non comedogenic, fragrance free, paraben free, soap and sulfate-free cleansers, allergy tested, dermatologist tested, and suitable for sensitive skin.













Discover a new way to help restore healthy looking skin






         Recommended routine for normal to dry skin.
        








A weakened skin barrier can result in signs of skin sensitivity such as dry skin and visible redness.

48% of the U.S. population has sensitive skin*. Do you?*L'Oréal 2016 A&U Study
Signs of Sensitive Skin


