The only system with Effaclar Duo to reduce up to 60% of acne in only 10 days. Visible results starting day 1
System includes: Effaclar Medicated Gel Cleanser (100ml), Effaclar Clarifying Solution (100ml), Effaclar Duo (20ml)
Use as a treatment for acne








