 Career History



Chief Executive Officer

                                    2017 - Current                


CURT Manufacturing LLC


                  Curt Manufacturing LLC manufactures, imports and distributes towing system products. Its products include Trailer Hitches, Towing Accessories, Specialized Towing, Trailer Balls, Ball Mounts, Cargo Management and Towing Electrical. The company offers American-made, custom-fit receiver hitches and wiring harnesses. Curt Manufacturing was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Eau Claire, WI.                




Chief Executive Officer

                                    2010 - 2016                


Rec Boat Holdings LLC


                  Part of Bénéteau SA, Rec Boat Holdings LLC is an American company located in Candillac, MI. The firm manufactures recreational and fishing boats. It was acquired by Bénéteau SA from Platinum Equity LLC on 23 Jun 14.                





